'''Tsutsumidori Entrance/Exit''' (つつみどおりでいりぐち) is an {{ill|Interchange (road)|en|Interchange (road)|WD=Q2376564|lt=interchange|1=Interchange (road)}} on the {{ill|Mukojima Route|en|Mukojima Route|WD=Q11667098|lt=Shuto Expressway Route 6 Mukojima Line|1=Mukojima Route}} located in {{ill|Sumida, Tokyo|en|Sumida, Tokyo|WD=Q235135|lt=Sumida City|1=Sumida, Tokyo}}, {{ill|Tokyo|en|Tokyo|WD=Q1490|lt=Tokyo|1=Tokyo}}. It is a {{ill|Interchange_(road)|ja|フルインターチェンジ|Interchange_(road)=Interchange_(road)|lt=full interchange|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Interchange_(road)|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to インターチェンジ|1=Interchange (road)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q2376564}} with both entrances and exits for traffic in both directions. Additionally, the neighboring {{ill|Mukojima Entrance/Exit|ja|向島出入口|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mukojima Entrance/Exit|1=Q10918115|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10918115}} (exits only) is also located within the Tsutsumidori area of Sumida Ward.

[[File:Tsutsumidori Ent 2.JPG|thumb|Tsutsumidori Entrance/Exit (Horikiri JCT direction)]]

